PrecisLeasing to the SASKATCHEWAN ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION (SEDCO), for a term of forty (40) years, of some 8,440 square metres of land situate on the grounds of Regina Airport, in the City of Regina, Saskatchewan, which are to be used as the site for the construction of a building offering industrial and office space for rent.
